      • setDepth

        public void setDepth(IInstrumentUpdateInfo updateInfo,
                     IDepthEntry[] buyDepth,
                     IDepthEntry[] sellDepth,
                     int depthLimit)
        Description copied from interface: IDepthFullUpdateMessage
        Adds depth information to the message.
        Specified by:
        setDepth in interface IDepthFullUpdateMessage
        Parameters:
        updateInfo - Update info of instrument whose depth entries are to be added.
        buyDepth - Buy side depth entries for the given instrument.
        sellDepth - Sell side depth entries for the given instrument.
        depthLimit - Maximum number of levels of depth to add to message. A value of 0 indicates unlimited depth.

      • setDetail

        public void setDetail(IInstrumentUpdateInfo updateInfo,
                      IDepthEntry[] buyDepth,
                      IDepthEntry[] sellDepth,
                      int depthLimit)
        Description copied from interface: IDepthFullUpdateMessage
        Adds detail information to the message.

        Note that it is the depth entries that are passed in. This is because each depth entry contains the list of detail entries at that price level - accessed using the IDepthEntry.getDetail() method.

        Specified by:
        setDetail in interface IDepthFullUpdateMessage
        Parameters:
        updateInfo - Update info of instrument whose depth entries are to be added.
        buyDepth - Buy side depth entries for the given instrument.
        sellDepth - Sell side depth entries for the given instrument.
        depthLimit - Maximum number of levels of detail to add to message. A value of 0 indicates unlimited detail.
